title: Check if an online animal medicine retailer is accredited

heading_context: Check if an online animal medicine retailer is accredited
chunks.html_content:
Check if a retailer is part of the Accredited Internet Retailer Scheme (AIRS).

Accredited sellers must prescribe the most appropriate medicine for the animal and advise customers how to use the medicine safely.
chunks.plain_content:

heading_context: Check if an online animal medicine retailer is accredited
chunks.html_content: This is a voluntary scheme. Retailers do not have to be accredited to sell animal medicines.
